### 1. **PCI ID Table Structure**

The driver defines PCI IDs in [`drivers/net/wireless/intel/iwlwifi/pcie/drv.c`](https://sourcegraph.sourcegraph.com/r/github.com/torvalds/linux/-/blob/drivers/net/wireless/intel/iwlwifi/pcie/drv.c?L34-L552). The 9260 card uses a **wildcard subdevice match**:

